{"tid":1754094,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不說, 連儂牆係今次選舉發揮極大作用","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T08:13:56.000Z","uid":12344,"like":89,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"0592d427596dfb59a16b42478ecf0ef8e13f7194","tid":1754094,"uid":12344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:01:46.000Z","msg":"要知道香港老一輩同師奶絕對多過我地後生仔好多, 佢地日日睇TVB, 係社區俾民建聯蛇齋餅糉<br />\n佢地唔會理自身以外發生咩事, 亦都冇渠道去知,但連儂牆就打破左呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n以我自己社區為例, 貼左好多文宣係馬會外圍, D廢老一開始都不停撕, 但慢慢佢地會睇下文宣上面寫既野, 接觸多左唔同既資訊, 開始懷疑電視上面講既野<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望大家, 文宣唔好停, 黎緊仲有好多選舉, 廢老師奶都係香港人, 要話俾佢地知香港發生緊咩事, 因為佢地真係唔知<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人加油!</span></strong>"},{"pid":"5c581e4107ebf3347f1610c07ced440ec90810d3","tid":1754094,"uid":204227,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:03:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日開始</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黎明行動</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宿一燒</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">麻包袋</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復連儂</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃色經濟</span>"},{"pid":"9a83b00ce81394ad90f45109d09a55ca7154ffff","tid":1754094,"uid":108337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:07:34.000Z","msg":"黃大仙真係靠晒師奶既例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec076fd0f43beb0305d9bf6b591658a9f93b527","tid":1754094,"uid":12344,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有文宣D字大隻D, 咁細隻廢老點睇</span>"},{"pid":"f27ae187d688a5b868a06b264aa9f806c2259766","tid":1754094,"uid":12344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d61d2dfb0ac8e4a402cbafed08e955c6dfc07b6","tid":1754094,"uid":46035,"like":1,"dis